  <prompt>
    Invoke the `researcher` subagent (per `.claude/agents/researcher.md`) to investigate whether
    `Microsoft.Extensions.AI.Testing` (or an equivalent Microsoft-shipped companion package to
    `Microsoft.Extensions.AI` v10.3.0) exists as a STABLE NuGet package providing `IChatClient`
    streaming mocks for `IAsyncEnumerable&lt;T&gt;`.

    The verdict drives Phase 1 P1.B1 (the `AsyncEnumerableHelpers` task — to be generated later):
    - "use Microsoft" → P1.B1 adds package reference to test csproj + thin shim
    - "hand-roll" → P1.B1 builds `Mocks/AsyncEnumerableHelpers.cs` from scratch

    Capture the verdict + supporting evidence to `decisions/D-01-async-enumerable-helper.md`.
    Apply design.md §5.1 decision criteria explicitly in the verdict.

    NO source-code or test changes. Pure investigation + decision capture.
  </prompt>

  <role>AI agent coordinating researcher subagent investigation; captures structured verdict.</role>

  <goal>
