    - Evidence: NuGet package names + versions checked, Microsoft Learn URLs, Microsoft.Extensions.AI GitHub sample paths or test-code paths inspected
    - Decision-criteria mapping per design.md §5.1 (stable version? streaming-mock-specific? sample-referenced? NSubstitute/Moq compatible?)
    - Implication for P1.B1 task acceptance criteria
  </goal>

